OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FSunny
OL,6,Fspells Thursday with a few showers
OL,7,Fpossible. A further rain band pushes
OL,8,Fnortheast on Friday. Bright spells and
OL,9,Fshowers again on Saturday.
